Benefit (DE / EN): Einstiegsgeld (DE) / Entry allowance for new employment (EN)
IDLB: B100019_LB_102713860
Requirements text (EN): * You receive citizen benefit before starting your new job. Unemployment is not a requirement.
* You must apply to your Jobcenter before actually starting your new job.
* Your new self-employment or new employment is suitable for overcoming your need for support in the future.
* The entry allowance is necessary for your integration into the general labor market.
* Your employment includes at least 15 hours per week.

Additional requirements for self-employment/start-up:

  * Positive assessment by the Jobcenter regarding 
    * Your personal suitability,
    * The economic viability of your self-employed activity.

